    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah that makes sense. it's like these data points are just behaving totally differently from the rest of the set, almost like they're following their own rules or something. do you think it could be heteroscedasticity, or is there some other way these outliers could be causing this kind of non-normal pattern?",
